2314210,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":48,"score":-39,"quote":{"pid":"26ab961447fe43acbec169aa61351d5c16b61503","tid":2314210,"uid":92299,"like":11,"dislike":123,"score":-112,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"邊個唔課金比峯b邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"轉個頭充公做警察薪金"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"黑警會有報應，有錢冇得使<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"希望有生之年見到佢哋有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb8c2cdfd0ea3b41cbd369fa99d0186cbc50bd0","tid":2314210,"uid":263944,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f573bf6909ec087e0c6e396ba49928f4000e2f52","tid":2314210,"uid":282801,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"#2,3,4都一早block咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"2345都block哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d4b9d1915351a2c4dda0d6e41a95365d8d8af6","tid":2314210,"uid":116560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"順便同埋港共講，封我律師樓既錢啦，間接講埋比世界知，就算d錢唔係個人戶口都無用，快d走資啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將公眾形象放係first priority就唔諗對家下一步做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"> #許智峯 #眾籌款項存在律師樓戶口<br />\n從丹麥轉到英國，吸入每一口自由的空氣，都是對自己的提醒，要用盡這邊的自由為香港發聲，亦要讓世界各國領袖看到，在遙遠的東方，有一座美麗城市正被港共暴政摧毀 ，但城裡的人仍昂首拒默沉，為自由而戰。我現在擁有的自由，就是我與世界一起抗擊暴政最強的武器。<br />\n當然港共可以對我、對外國政治家、對全世界繼續譴責抹黑，但全世界都清楚看到公義在哪一方，戰狼外交只會繼續被世界圍堵。<br />\n至於我及全家人的銀行戶口被凍結，明顯是政權以經濟壓迫作政治報復，以連坐法打壓我家人以逼害反對的聲音。政權甚至到現在亦無膽公開說是否正在調查我家人、關於什麼罪行等，根本是理虧，旨在包庇警方濫用行為。政權以為這樣可打壓異己，卻不知道做法直接衝擊全世界對香港銀行體系及司法制度的信心，自我攬炒。<br />\n關心我生計的朋友，請你們不用擔心，我在這邊有朋友可短暫依靠，可挨過去。我從來非常謹慎，絕不會輕易為自己眾籌，除非是為了香港、為公眾做事。大家的好意，我銘記於心。<br />\n至於有關我去年發起就私人檢控抗警暴的眾籌，款項從來均全數存在律師樓戶口，核數報告亦已全面公開，款項與我個人及家人戶口完全無關，在此以正視聽。<br />\n#許智峯_FB</span>"},{"pid":"79ecaac11f04ec93154a132275b7d993760e375b","tid":2314210,"uid":31835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"消失的234<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a0f9ca8bf3d2cbbae65c3793dd0e8df9a54de5","tid":2314210,"uid":340189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a5cedb64861a5542b03b72ef9040e5c71df8ca9","tid":2314210,"uid":315771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842a77c93db12a453c4faa91825ee77b59205de3","tid":2314210,"uid":92299,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"84f361e79892b088fa1de3292aed9ec951759f0a","tid":2314210,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":48,"score":-39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"轉個頭充公做警察薪金"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"黑警會有報應，有錢冇得使<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"希望有生之年見到佢哋有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:16:41.000Z","msg":"大把野大家可以做<br />\n<br />\n香港人堅持<br />\n繼續所有戰線"},{"pid":"b52508305a8b05213d9533531a59b9ca2853d1f5","tid":2314210,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2a5cedb64861a5542b03b72ef9040e5c71df8ca9","tid":2314210,"uid":315771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842a77c93db12a453c4faa91825ee77b59205de3","tid":2314210,"uid":92299,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"84f361e79892b088fa1de3292aed9ec951759f0a","tid":2314210,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":48